theme_NFL <- function () { 
    theme_bw(base_size=10, base_family="sans") %+replace% 
        theme(
            axis.text.x=element_text(angle=30,
                                     hjust=1,
                                     vjust=1),
            panel.background  = element_blank(),
            plot.background = element_blank(),
            panel.grid = element_blank(),
            complete=TRUE
        )
}
